The three binaries are for different CPUs of Apple computers:

- petrify-intel is for the Intel-based Macs (only the recent hardware)
- petrify-ppc is for PowerPC-based Macs (only the older hardware)
- petrify-universal is for both platforms and should be the format of choice 
  (see http://www.apple.com/universal)

